AMERICANS (2) Bowater Inc., IBM, CANADIANS (1) Derlan, BANKS (2) Natl.
Australia, Standard Chrtd., BREWERS &amp; DISTILLERS (2) Greenalls 5.95pc Pf,
Vaux, BUILDING MATERIALS (5) BMSS, Breedon, Cape, Erith, Hewetson, BUSINESS
