FT  22 AUG 92 / Markets (At A Glance): New postal account from C&amp;G
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Cheltenham &amp; Gloucester launches a new postal account today, the London
deposit account, which is a tiered version of the London Share Account.
Investors can choose to have interest paid monthly though this will be at a
lower rate than annual interest. The minimum transaction amount is Pounds
250. The account is advertised as instant access but withdrawals will be
subject to a penalty of seven days interest.
The minimum deposit is Pounds 5,000, compared with Pounds 2,500 in the Share
Account. There are three tiers. Interest rates start at 9.6 per cent gross
(annual) and 9.11 per cent (monthly) and the top rate is 10.2 per cent gross
on Pounds 25,000 or more (annual) and 9.66 per cent (monthly).
