FT  22 AUG 92 / UK Company News: Boscombe Property rises to Pounds 351,000
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Profits before tax of Boscombe Property rose to Pounds 351,221 for the 12
months ended March 31, a 43 per cent improvement over the previous year's
Pounds 245,450.
The results were helped by a rise in gross rental income from Pounds 703,980
to Pounds 813,768. Available profits emerged at Pounds 265,748 (Pounds
185,395), equal to earnings per share of 262.25p (181.9p). Dividends
totalling 180p (130p) have already been paid.
