on capital employed over the past 12 months was 20.1 per cent, up 1.1 per
cent on 1991 full year, while return on equity after tax rose to 22.5 per
cent over the same period compared with 21.4 per cent for the full year of
1991.
The company improved sales in all areas with a particularly large growth in
renal care equipment to SKr2.236bn from SKr2.075bn.
