<HEADLINE>
FT  21 AUG 92 / UK Company News: Tactel boosts ICI sales
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Imperial Chemical Industries has captured 10 per cent of the European market
for hosiery fibres with a new product launched 18 months ago.
The use of Tactel nylon microfibre in 350m items of hosiery this year means
sales of about Pounds 20m to ICI.
Tactel is a nylon microfibre and buyers include all the big manufacturers of
hosiery in Europe.
</TEXT>
