<HEADLINE>
FT  21 AUG 92 / UK Company News: Changes planned at Embassy
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Embassy Property, the USM-quoted property developer, housebuilder and
construction group, is proposing a share placing, a rights issue and a
restructuring of group borrowings.
The placing is of 56m new ordinary shares at 5p to raise Pounds 2.5m net
which will result in a change of control of the company. The 3-for-4 rights
issue of 5.73m shares at 5p will raise some Pounds 280,000.
The directors are of the opinion that the proposals will place Embassy in a
position to take new opportunities which will arise in the commercial
property market over the next two to three years.
</TEXT>
